parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the basement storage compartment doors can cause the doors to open while driving, leading to accidents, loss of contents, and potential harm to other drivers.
symptoms: The storage compartment doors open unexpectedly while driving
the doors do not stay closed
the doors are difficult to open and close
and the contents of the compartment are exposed to the road.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The loose steering and unstable handling can cause the vehicle to sway or drift out of its lane, increasing the risk of accidents or loss of control, especially at high speeds.
symptoms: The vehicle is difficult to keep in a straight line
sways or drifts out of its lane
has too much play in the steering
and has a tendency to wander or float on the road.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The excessive brightness of the dashboard, particularly at night, can reduce the driver's night vision, increasing the risk of accidents and compromising safety.
symptoms: The dashboard lights are too bright
making it difficult to drive safely at night.
